oviding leadership during outages, and scheduling fire drills for fail-overs. >>> https://www.flexjobs.com/HostedJob.aspx?id=1090184&utm_campaign=website&utm_source=sendgrid.com&utm_medium=email Success Manager - Marketing Cloud | Salesforce Success manager needed for a full-time, remote option position requiring a bachelor's degree, five+ years' professional experience, exceptional communication skills, multi-tasking ability. Will manage projects, build relationships. >>> https://www.flexjobs.com/HostedJob.aspx?id=1091369&utm_campaign=website&utm_source=sendgrid.com&utm_medium=email Biology Video Developer | Nagwa Video developer sought for a remote position requiring a biology BA/BS, two+ years' relevant experience, English fluency, and previous video-related experience. Will conduct research, generate and implement plans, record and edit digital footage.>>> https://www.flexjobs.com/HostedJob.aspx?id=1091197&utm_campaign=website&utm_source=sendgrid.com&utm_medium=email Bilingual Telephonic RN Care Manager | Humana Evaluate members needs, facilitate interaction with resources, and guide members/families. Must be an RN and have at least three yrs' clinical exp. This is a full-time, work from home position. 40 hrs/wk. >>> https://www.flexjobs.com/HostedJob.aspx?id=1091175&utm_campaign=website&utm_source=sendgrid.com&utm_medium=email Underwriter | loanDepot Underwrite residential mortgage loans and evaluate loans in order to maximize organizational profit and minimize risk or loss. Must have 3+ years of successful FHA, VA and conventional underwriting experience plus a HS diploma. Home-based.>>> https://www.flexjobs.com/HostedJob.aspx?id=1091404&utm_campaign=website&utm_source=sendgrid.com&utm_medium=email Event and Community Coordinator | Holo Functions include designing event processes, recruiting volunteers, project managing hackathons & meetups, launching marketing initiatives, & coordinating event logistics. Community organizing/management experience required. Mo